{
  "title": "Tender Yeasty Indian Chickpeas Chana Masala",
  "description": "A light and flavorful Indian dish featuring yeasty chickpeas in a rich and spicy tomato sauce, served with a side of gherkin relish and render fat, perfect for a solo dinner.",
