      "amount": "1 teaspoon",
      "notes": "to taste"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat the render fat in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until it is translucent and starting to brown.",
    "Add the yeast and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chickpeas, tomato puree, garam masala, cumin, coriander, and salt, and stir well to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 20 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Stir in the gherkin relish and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning as needed.",
    "Serve the chana masala hot, garnished with additional gherkin relish if desired."
